# Summary
This documentation explains how to set up Single Sign-On (SSO) integration between OneLogin and Amplitude for Scholarship, Growth, and Enterprise plan customers, detailing the step-by-step process of configuring the SAML 2.0 application in OneLogin and uploading the metadata file to Amplitude.

